# Second Brain — System Context

**Second Brain** is a separate personal AI assistant system (FastAPI on Google Cloud Run, NVIDIA L4 GPU, europe-west1).
It is **not** AK_system — AK_system (Next.js + tRPC) is a partial implementation of Second Brain's concepts.
Wiki: https://wiki.bachar-israeli.com/#second-brain/overview

## Infrastructure
- FastAPI · Cloud Run (4 vCPU, 16 GiB, 1× NVIDIA L4, concurrency 80) · Python 3.11
- Gemini API · pyannote.audio (GPU diarization) · WhatsApp (Meta Cloud API + Baileys) · Google Drive
- Deploy: GitHub Actions → Docker → Artifact Registry → Cloud Run

## Core Services (~30 internal)
| Layer | Services |
|---|---|
| AI | gemini_service, audio_pipeline, pyannote_service, speaker_identity_service, expert_analysis_service (3 personas: Sinek/Tech/Adler), conversation_engine |
| Communication | whatsapp_provider, meta_whatsapp_service, group_listener_service (Baileys) |
| Memory | drive_memory_service, knowledge_base_service, context_writer_service |
| Scheduling | task_service, calendar_service (ICS: Outlook + Google), daily_meeting_summary_service, kids_schedule_service |
| External | health_service, weather_service (Open-Meteo), flight_search_service (SerpAPI) |
| Output | infographic_generator (Pillow), pdf_service (ReportLab RTL), architecture_audit_service |

## Scheduled Jobs
| Job | Schedule |
|---|---|
| Morning Calendar Briefing | 07:00 Israel |
| Pre-Meeting Briefing | Every 5 min |
| Daily Meeting Summary | 20:00 Israel |
| Health-Meeting Correlation | 21:00 Israel Sun–Thu |
| Weekly Architecture Audit | Friday 13:00 Israel |
| Task Reminder Poller | Every 1 min |

## Key API Endpoints
- `GET /health`, `GET /version`
- `GET|POST /webhook` (WhatsApp), `POST /analyze` (multimodal), `POST /group-message`
- `/api/admin/*` — auth (OTP→JWT), dashboard, speakers, transcripts, context, settings
- `/cursor-inbox`, `/cursor-result`, `/bridge-heartbeat` (Cursor Bridge)

